<div class="modal fade" id="signup-modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="signup-modal">
  <div id="signup">
    <div class="signup-wrapper">
      <header>
        <h1>회원가입</h1>
        <h4>지금 회원가입을 하면 <br class="visible-xs">
          <%= image_tag "g-button.png", class: "go-symbol", alt: "나누고 단추", size: "20x20" %>
          단추 5,000개를 드립니다.
        </h4>
      </header>
      <section class="social-connect">
        <ul>
          <li class="facebook">
            <%= link_to omniauth_authorize_path(resource_name, :facebook) do %>
              <span>Facebook 계정으로 가입하기</span>
            <% end %>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section class="sign-in">
        <div class="seperator">
          <hr />
          <span>또는</span>
        </div>
        <div id="js-error-messages" class="result"></div>
        <%= form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => user_registration_path, :html => { :id => "signup-box" }, :format => :json, :remote => true, authenticity_token: true) do |f| %>
          <div class="fields">
            <div class="form-group">
              <%= f.email_field :email, placeholder: "이메일을 입력해 주세요.", autofocus: true, autocomplete: "off" %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="signup">
            <%= f.submit "회원가입" %>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </section>
      <section class="text-center">
        <div>이미 nanuGO 계정이 있으신가요? <a href="#" class="js-modal-signin">로그인하기</a></div>
        <div>인증메일을 다시 받고 싶으신가요? <a href="#" class="js-modal-confirmation">인증메일 재전송</a></div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
